{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeButtonComponentTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of buttons"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ButtonComponentT